= <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> Planned Coup Discovered!

With the presidential elections approaching, Prussian Minister of the Interior Carl Severing has ordered emergency searches of all <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazi</span> and <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> offices throughout Prussia.

During the raids, damning evidence was uncovered: the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">Nazi</span> Party headquarters in Munich had ordered <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> units to be placed on high alert for election day. In the event of a Hindenburg victory, these units were prepared to launch a coup d'état, including the planned seizure of military installations and weaponry.

The revelation has sent shockwaves through the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span> coalition. [? if interior_minister == "Wirth": Interior Minister Joseph Wirth of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> is pushing hard for immediate action?][? if interior_minister_party != "Wirth": The Interior Minister seems hesitant, worried about Conservative backlash. ?]
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
- @push_federal_ban: Use our government position to push for a nationwide <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> ban!
- @coalition_consensus: Seek coalition consensus before acting on the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> threat.
- @prussian_only: Limit action to Prussia to avoid splitting the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span>.

@push_federal_ban
on-arrival: player_choice_sa_ban = "federal"
go-to: sa_ban_burgerblock_succeeds == 1 ? outcome_success : (sa_ban_partial == 1 ? outcome_partial : outcome_failure)

@coalition_consensus
on-arrival: player_choice_sa_ban = "consensus"  
