@prussian_only
on-arrival: player_choice_sa_ban = "prussian"; sa_strength *= 0.85; sa_militancy -= 0.05; prussian_police_loyalty += 0.05; dvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.05; dnvp_burgerblock_dissent += 0.1; left_dissent -= 5

We limit our response to Prussia alone, maintaining the existing <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> ban there while avoiding a direct confrontation within the <span style="color: #4A5C2A;">Bürgerblock</span>. This cautious approach preserves coalition unity but allows the <span style="color: #7A3C00;">**SA**</span> to continue operating freely in other states.

The Conservative partners seem relieved, but the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> and parts of our own membership are frustrated by what they see as insufficient action against the Nazi threat.

- @end: The coalition holds, for now.

